Package: coursemap
Type: Package
Title: Course Dependency Map Visualization
Version: 0.1.5
Authors@R: c(person("Kenji", "Sato", email = "mail@kenjisato.jp", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A tool to visualize course dependencies from Quarto/Markdown documents.
    This package provides R bindings for the Rust-based course-map tool,
    allowing easy integration with Quarto documents and R environments.
